msg: Ev2 shims: make sure the correct start and set revision handlers are called
(start_edit_func_t): Remove pool parameter, and root baton output param.
(ev2_edit_baton): Add the extra_baton, remove the root_baton, start_edit func
and baton, as well as the target_revision func and baton.
(ev2_set_target_revision): Call the provided target revision function.
(delta_from_editor): Take and "extra baton" and store it for later
(editor_from_delta): Construct and return an extra baton.
(svn_editor__insert_shims): Provide a pointer to pass around the extra baton.
